The paper discusses the use of deep learning and convolutional neural networks (cs.CV) for visual classification tasks, specifically using dynamic vision sensors (DVS) to improve performance in high-speed applications. The paper also mentions the use of hardware accelerators (cs.ET) and FPGA implementation (cs.AR) for prototyping and testing. Additionally, the paper discusses the use of VHDL and HLS for circuit and computation block descriptions (cs.LG).
